        <item>
            <title>旧款 MacBook Pro 荧幕疑入尘致损坏，外媒：「2018 年起发售的 5 个型号受影响」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/18/macbook-pro-dustgate/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=macbook-pro-dustgate</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/18/macbook-pro-dustgate/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 07:33:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1204942</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 最近有多款 MacBook Pro 的外国用家反映电脑荧幕出现非正常故障的情况，疑因机内有灰尘进入所致。</p><p>近日有不少国外用户反映，当 MacBook Pro 荧幕在某些角度时，会出现灰紫色线条的情况而引起热议。有维修人员猜测，因机身在长期使用下，累积在萤幕与键盘间的灰尘会随着萤幕多次开合而从铰链缝隙渗入，导致荧幕出现损坏。用家将 MacBook Pro 萤幕入尘损坏的事件称为「灰尘门」（Dustgate）。</p><p>维修人员展示一些入尘后故障的 MacBook Pro 电脑。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1205045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-496x580.jpg" alt="" width="496" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-496x580.jpg 496w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-769x900.jpg 769w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-768x899.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0.jpg 959w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 496px" /></a></p><p>据外媒报道，主要受影响的机款为 2018 年到 2020 年推出的 MacBook Pro 型号，包括 A1989、A2251、A2289、A2141、A2338，其中又以 A2141 出现入尘情况的次数最多。但提出此问题的技术人员 Ricky Panesar 指 2016 年开始发售的机款都采近似设计，所以都有机会受到影响。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1205046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-1-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-1-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-1-768x509.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/960x0-1.jpg 959w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>目前，Apple 尚未针对此事作出任何回应，受影响的用户正等待解决方案或更换装置的机会。外媒建议上述 MacBook Pro 机款的用户尽量避免在多灰尘的地方使用，并定期清洁电脑，预防灰尘堆积，避免萤幕受损。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/jaymcgregor/2023/11/14/new-macbook-pro-dustgate-problem-is-breaking-apple-laptop-displays/?sh=5f44c6d3641c">forbes</a>、<a href="https://www.timesnownews.com/technology-science/macbook-pro-users-report-dustgate-issue-causing-screen-malfunctions-article-105246388">timesnownews</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

