            <title>韩国版「模拟市民」采用 UE5 引擎　《inZOI》人物建模符合亚洲观感</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/18/inzoi-sims-korean/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=inzoi-sims-korean</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/18/inzoi-sims-korean/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 06:50:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[inZOI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[模拟市民]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1205542</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Unreal Engine 5 推出之后，其性能一直都受到相当好评，可以用于制作极为逼真的场景。最近有韩国开发商就公布了采用 UE5 的生活模拟游戏，整体充满韩风设计。<br /><span id="more-1205542"></span></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113105006_1853w.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="405" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1205545" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113105006_1853w.jpg 720w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113105006_1853w-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 720px" /></p><p>在 G-Star 2023 上，开发商 Krafton 公布了名为 inZOI（인조이）的游戏新作，它采用的 Unreal Engine 5 使其在画面效果上相当真实，在光源和反射上的处理，包括物件和空间，以及服饰等等都相当精细，更可以对物品深入自订。而游戏性方面，inZOI 类似《模拟市民》的玩法，不过就提供更高的自由度，角色也可以在城市中不同部分穿梭。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_82297"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YDDug3K3Uts?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>对比欧美风格的《模拟市民》，inZOI 则彻头彻尾重现现代韩国，城市中的街道以至人物设计等都符合韩式美学，对于亚洲玩家来说应该会更有亲切感。目前游戏仍然在开发当中，并未有正式的推出时间公布，不过以他们已经成功引起话题的情况看来，可能不用等太久就会有进一步消息了。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113104248_5700w.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="405" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1205544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113104248_5700w.jpg 720w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/20231113104248_5700w-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 720px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.thisisgame.com/webzine/news/nboard/4/?n=180419?n">This is game</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

